{"word":"ὑπομιμνῄσκω","slug":"ὑπομιμνῄσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑπομιμνῄσϰω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπό\">ὑπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μιμνῄσκω\">μιμνῄσκω</a></el>] ‘cause to be in the mind in a time subsequent to earlier experience or awareness’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b>remind <a href='B:500 14:26'>J 14:26</a>; <a href='B:620 2:14'>2 Ti 2:14</a>; <a href='B:630 3:1'>Tit 3:1</a>; <a href='B:680 1:12'>2 Pt 1:12</a>; <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 5</a>; bring up <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 10</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> our ‘I am reminded of’) <b>remember, think of <a href='B:490 22:61'>Lk 22:61</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπομένω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπομνῆσαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}